==English==
===Etymology===
From the name of a perfume created by [[w:François Coty|François Coty]] in 1917. French [[Chypre]] means [[Cyprus]]. 

===Noun===
'''chypre''' (''plural'' [[chypres]])

# family of [[fragrance]]s build on a base consisting of [[bergamot]], [[oakmoss]] and [[labdanum]].
# a [[perfume]] with such a fragrance